      "date": "2013-02-05 22:50:42.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nNote, if there is no reason to make patches dependent on each other, they should be submitted from separate branches, an you can use something like topgit at your side if you want to test them together.  This allows the patches to be tested and landed more efficiently in Gerrit, since the individual patches need to be refreshed/inspected/tested less often due to external dependencies.",
